How do you prove that your digital assistant works the way you want it to work? You need to provide a series of test cases that will allow anyone to test your digital assistant and verify that it works correctly. 

<strong>This is a required section for your digital assistant</strong>

In the space below, record all keywords and keyword combinations that will cause your digital assistant to produce a unique output. Use the following format:

<br/>
